<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[WSJ - EN-US - opinion]]></title><link/> https://www.wsj.com/news/opinion <atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/wsj/en-us/opinion" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[WSJ - EN-US - opinion - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RS集线器</generator><webmaster>i@diygod.me (DIYgod)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 8 月 14 日星期一 13:16:10 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[Pepper...and Salt]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div>无效的<!-- data-module-name="article.app/lib/module/wsj/breadcrumbs" --><main id="main" role="main"><div class="wsj-article-headline-wrap crawler"></div><div class="articleLead" itemprop="articleLead" data-sbid="SB11667163785710763363504590144713494957800"></div><div class="articleBody" data-sbid="SB11667163785710763363504590144713494957800"><div class="clearfix bylineWrap"><time class="timestamp article__timestamp flexbox__flex--1">美国东部时间 2023 年 8 月 14 日上午 12:00 </time></div><div subscriptions-actions="" subscriptions-display="NOT data.noSharing"><div class="share-bar"><amp-social-share type="system" width="72" height="24" data-param-url="https://www.wsj.com/articles/pepper-and-salt-c894a8e"></amp-social-share></div></div><section subscriptions-section="content"><div class="media-object scope-
